Package org.openlca.core.database.references

package org.openlca.core.database.references
  • Interface Summary
    Interface
    Description
    IReferenceSearch<T extends CategorizedDescriptor>
    A reference search is the inverse of a usage search: while a usage search searches in which other entities an entity is used, a reference search searches which other entities are referenced from an entity.
